722d625d-e9c8-4937-8fd8-424ad87ef7cc.title: Wizard Cromperty
722d625d-e9c8-4937-8fd8-424ad87ef7cc.text:
Hello there. My name is Cromperty. I am a Wizard,
and an inventor.

3aeeb926-fa03-4b5d-ac76-66ada81103e9.title: <player>
3aeeb926-fa03-4b5d-ac76-66ada81103e9.text:
You must be <player>. My good friend Sedridor has
told me about you. As both wizard and inventor, he has
aided me in my great invention!

options.text: Two jobs? That's got to be tough.
Can you teleport me to the Rune Essence?

88255f50-aabd-4337-8883-421e21f53b81.title: <player>
88255f50-aabd-4337-8883-421e21f53b81.text: Two jobs? That's got to be tough.

dcca923d-82ff-4d61-8ad6-af137a6e2934.title: Wizard Cromperty
dcca923d-82ff-4d61-8ad6-af137a6e2934.text:
Not when you combine them it isn't! I invent MAGIC
things!

options.text: Well, I shall leave you to your inventing.

3afc2bdf-6a06-49c1-9e33-9f911b289378.title: Wizard Cromperty
3afc2bdf-6a06-49c1-9e33-9f911b289378.text:
Ah! My latest invention is my patent pending
teleportation block! It emits a low level magical signal,
that will allow me to locate it anywhere in the world,
and teleport anything

4f0e3ed0-d7e6-46f7-ac7a-5919845963ea.title: Wizard Cromperty
4f0e3ed0-d7e6-46f7-ac7a-5919845963ea.text:
directly to it! I hope to revolutionise the entire
teleportation system! Don't you think I'm great? Uh, I
mean it's great?

options.text: So where is the other block?

c70e2ab9-27c6-44dc-b098-7970bb2004db.title: <player>
c70e2ab9-27c6-44dc-b098-7970bb2004db.text: So where is the other block?

6e2a61c9-4858-4198-a901-327691067307.title: Wizard Cromperty
6e2a61c9-4858-4198-a901-327691067307.text:
Well... Hmm. I would guess somewhere between here
and the Wizards' Tower in Misthalin. All I know is that
it hasn't got there yet as the wizards there would have
contacted me.

6e8a7770-34a0-4db6-b9d2-22d28cb725c3.title: Wizard Cromperty
6e8a7770-34a0-4db6-b9d2-22d28cb725c3.text:
The Gielinor Parcel Delivery Team. They come very
highly recommended. Their motto is: 'We aim to deliver
your stuff at some point after you have paid us!'

06c003ae-28ff-4c3d-ae92-a2de2dc1b5d6.title: Wizard Cromperty
06c003ae-28ff-4c3d-ae92-a2de2dc1b5d6.text:
Yes it is isn't it? Forgive me for feeling a little smug,
this is a major breakthrough in the field of teleportation!

f48f1ebc-59c4-499b-a3d7-81b2d56d7a8b.title: <player>
f48f1ebc-59c4-499b-a3d7-81b2d56d7a8b.text: Can you teleport me to the Rune Essence?
